feedback.Message: The system is easy to use and very helpful.
I wish there were more resources linked in the course page.
I like the alerts for low GPA, it keeps me on track.
Course registration was smoother this semester, thank you!
Can we have notifications for prerequisite issues?
The dashboard gives a good overview of my progress.
Sometimes the page is slow, maybe it needs optimization.
Great idea to color code course statuses!
Can we add a comment box for each course?
I really appreciate the GPA tracking and summaries.
